{{about|a Syriac Orthodox saint|the primate of the Church of the East (159–171)|Abraham (bishop)|the last Mesopotamin Bishop in India|Abraham of Angamaly}}

'''Mor Abraham''' is a [[saint]] of the [[Syriac Orthodox Church]]. His [[feast day]] is November 15.

